{"tid":2409811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"818 未經批准遊行案今日開審 民主派將挑戰公安條例違憲 國際警務專家將作為辯方證人作供 預料本案會上訴至終審法院","createTime":"2021-02-16T06:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T12:16:07.000Z","uid":292499,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6ee5bb5b718da703e8a19ee0cc852fd9e7ebde","tid":2409811,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"更重要的是《公安條例》下警方禁止和平遊行的權力連同上訴機制，首次全面遭到違憲挑戰，對日後行使集會自由隨時有深遠影響。據知，辯方找來監警會前國際專家小組成員Clifford Stott撰寫專家報告。審訊明天繼續。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n辯方提出違憲挑戰，包括把<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">組織或參與和平集會遊行訂為罪行，是過度限制自由</span></span></strong>。而<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">警方禁止遊行的權力違憲，尤其當集會遊行目的是批評警方，警方涉利益衝突和有偏頗之嫌。</span></span></strong>同時，辯方亦質疑<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">上訴委員會制度是否公平公正公開。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/IR6MGTTU5JEJXBYEGLFJSOIHHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FIR6MGTTU5JEJXBYEGLFJSOIHHI%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=72eac265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FIR6MGTTU5JEJXBYEGLFJSOIHHI%2F&h=4578e5a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/IR6MGTTU5JEJXBYEGLFJSOIHHI/</a>"},{"pid":"03bbd8edc19f80d6cd25b94b2ec0a377ff4a93d6","tid":2409811,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9fb6d7b4bdb01d70cb7849188455ae3b17edb3","tid":2409811,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc